Adams claimed (autobiography) that Wenger threw his medal in the bin when Arsenal lost the 2001 FA Cup final to #LFC<br />
<br />
&ldquo;Don&rsquo;t trust too much what Tony Adams says,&rdquo; Wenger said. &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know. I don&rsquo;t remember. I am not separated from football, I am completely in football and I watch the game that is on in the night but I don&rsquo;t look back, what we have won, what we have done and what we have lost. I am always [looking] forward. It is about human beings, human experiences and shared emotions.&rdquo;

